{"tid":2460500,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"林 夕: 不 吃 這 一 套，中 國 吃 什 麼 ?","createTime":"2021-03-25T01:18:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T05:58:16.000Z","uid":364767,"like":1375,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":115,"replies":[{"pid":"ccb91168fdf703e761aeebb763d67074b961b30c","tid":2460500,"uid":364767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T01:18:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20210325/PCDHAVQK65HNLGSL46L2DGJ2WE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20210325%2FPCDHAVQK65HNLGSL46L2DGJ2WE%2F&d=G6FzB8XOFkGMVaf%2BSD5%2Fxiq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=a14c8c7e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20210325%2FPCDHAVQK65HNLGSL46L2DGJ2WE%2F&h=5bb33267\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20210325/PCDHAVQK65HNLGSL46L2DGJ2WE/</a><br />\n<br />\n嗌交部代表為要平視世界，強國跟美國霸權會談，原來就是靠吵的。發言時向着對方狂噴口水，幾千cc唾液酸度爆表，三分是測試拜登的核酸劑，七分是說給中國老百姓聽的興奮劑。<br />\n<br />\n楊潔篪超時發言十七分鐘，憑一句：「中國人不吃這一套」爆紅，小粉紅吃足了勁，勝過貪官吃香喝辣。<br />\n<br />\n中國人不吃這一套，究竟吃什麼？多着，十四億隻手指數不完。「民以食為天」果然不是浪得虛名。<br />\n<br />\n大主席講脫貧攻堅，講稿寫手都不忘吃，硬是加上一句「撒胡椒麵」，要替「熱乾麵」加油，不吃包子了，聽到飢民口水直流。好死不死的，簡化字吃「麵」化為吃「面」，嚇得人吃手手，原來最愛吃的一套，是吃面子維生。<br />\n<br />\n何止背脊向天皆可吃，「吃」字構詞特多，什麼都可以吃：吃癟、吃虧、吃苦、吃醋、吃緊、吃重、吃力、吃牌、吃胡、吃裏扒外，連犯事都要吃官司；總之吃飽，就是人權。<br />\n<br />\n吃什麼就變什麼，狗改不了吃屎，吃光了沙漠長出來的髮菜，吃到了北京變火星，讓市民吃沙塵暴，讓鄰近東北南亞地區吃霧霾。吃野味吃出了當年的沙士。<br />\n<br />\n靠山吃山，靠水吃水，從古時已吃喝不分。光盤行動吃到碟子只剩油光，糧食輸入大國，實際還要吃美國大豆，人沒得吃，豬豬都要吃豆豆。不買美帝的，就買俄羅斯的豬，結果吃出一場豬瘟。吃不了美帝晶片，華為大老闆轉型養豬。這動物農莊就不用吃西北風。<br />\n<br />\n還有，食言。 何解？吃古代異體字為「喫」，不管說文解字怎麼解，拆字後，掐指一算，即係專門吃契約，把合約精神吃進肚裏，吃掉中英聯合聲明，消化後變成並無現實意義的歷史文件，排泄出來讓人吃驚，良心都被狗吃了。<br />\n<br />\n吃過了台灣金鑽鳳梨，優惠台灣農民政策，出地出錢，吃掉了種子加技術，最後海南廣東人大吃山寨金鑽鳳梨，讓你吃癟。高薪招聘台積電員工，要偷吃半導體技術。最後還要吃進台灣，你吃硬不吃軟，就吃我一拳，講了七十年也不會口吃。<br />\n<br />\n其實中國自己也不吃這一套，身為戰狼，吃相太難看，當然用咬的，用噬的，四處亂咬，就是大外交。捷克前議長要訪台，發恐嚇信嚇得老人家間接死於心臟病。法國議員又要赴台一行，又再嚴重警告法國會吃不了兜着走。<br />\n胃口那麼大，真是吃飽撐着沒事幹。<br />\n<br />\n共匪再四圍搞搞震，遲早連屎都無得吃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb4145cd84b20db25c283b30c5c2e5dc85e641d9","tid":2460500,"uid":39710,"like":178,"dislike":0,"score":178,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T01:23:06.000Z","msg":"中国人吃套套算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"575c64ca0e56d34fc36766638bcd678038e770ce","tid":2460500,"uid":168138,"like":336,"dislike":0,"score":336,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T01:24:31.000Z","msg":"驚西咩<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPzQPoBffwS9MmBKJpUowuMgKFBvXG2KyKpJtrxS4kGCj?filename=pcR1Sv6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpcR1Sv6.jpg&h=a7743cac&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"43708e82707f2edab8210c654bcf6dd52b690f23","tid":2460500,"uid":67816,"like":228,"dislike":2,"score":226,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T01:28:04.000Z","msg":"好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過睇到個吃字好怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f6d996e77315c45edf3462938d8f149dd6b3443","tid":2460500,"uid":198389,"like":168,"dislike":0,"score":168,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T01:28:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmX7wdJydrc5T6BL93cTxzZkhtmbpkonW9JrMAUmjhJ6Ph?filename=pYUnBY5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpYUnBY5.jpg&h=1e27d78f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a8368bd4f82d8edf5e077e5a1e51829f40f00eda","tid":2460500,"uid":90615,"like":63,"dislike":0,"score":63,"quote":{"pid":"575c64ca0e56d34fc36766638bcd678038e770ce","tid":2460500,"uid":168138,"like":336,"dislike":0,"score":336,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T01:24:31.000Z","msg":"驚西咩<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pcR1Sv6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpcR1Sv6.jpg&h=a7743cac&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T01:28:34.000Z","msg":"我剩係屌范冰冰唔食飯都活一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b72ab0c4f3df4ab354a9d2ac31f56d3edb8241d","tid":2460500,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T01:29:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deacee9276aade09c74b26f6ef2ea11ac61834d1","tid":2460500,"uid":63154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T01:35:49.000Z","msg":"吃屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0f1760ee12b7e65caa42a216ccc95e74592a4d3","tid":2460500,"uid":59511,"like":64,"dislike":0,"score":64,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T01:39:27.000Z","msg":"的確，中國人係唔食談判呢一套，佢哋接受嘅係強權單方面壓迫。"},{"pid":"92f46f4c9d7e593ffa96a6e68a929557445e15d4","tid":2460500,"uid":393145,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T01:39:31.000Z","msg":"連你個名都吃咗<br />\n變佚名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"940eb8223f3ac84787bca7aacf29752eacbca1c0","tid":2460500,"uid":387826,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T01:46:23.000Z","msg":"陶傑：口腔期<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c033ef44d6308404fba107ccfdf43be548a15352","tid":2460500,"uid":28759,"like":108,"dislike":1,"score":107,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T03:26:03.000Z","msg":"林夕文筆<br />\n由個吃字屌中国人用字曖昧、行事多餘、惹事生非 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13a5a5202b95fa3122548f84e07326870a2fab60","tid":2460500,"uid":45523,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T03:28:56.000Z","msg":"屌 好精彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"005dd7f58841b35b545e478e6851fa65c23bd6d6","tid":2460500,"uid":45523,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"a8368bd4f82d8edf5e077e5a1e51829f40f00eda","tid":2460500,"uid":90615,"like":63,"dislike":0,"score":63,"quote":{"pid":"575c64ca0e56d34fc36766638bcd678038e770ce","tid":2460500,"uid":168138,"like":336,"dislike":0,"score":336,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T01:24:31.000Z","msg":"驚西咩<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pcR1Sv6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpcR1Sv6.jpg&h=a7743cac&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T01:28:34.000Z","msg":"我剩係屌范冰冰唔食飯都活一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T03:29:31.000Z","msg":"而家佢副尊容你都啱？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d881be590312fc2315ffb41bd3d332bd3855e57c","tid":2460500,"uid":106641,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T03:31:55.000Z","msg":"中國乜都食，連人都可以食得津津有味，呢啲就係傳統中華文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[食好野] 中國自古就是食人族社會 滅絕人性的中華食人傳統<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/517176\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/517176</a><br />\n<br />\n劉仲敬：愛沙尼亞人和烏克蘭人覺得跟斯大林同志比，希特勒已經很仁慈。諸夏各民族有更多的理由認為，跟中國侵略者比起來，蘇聯非常文明。中國人不僅是全世界最大最古老的食人族，而且是全世界唯一不以為恥反以為榮的食人族。阿茲特克人雖然在前一方面跟中國人並駕齊驅，在後一方面卻大大落伍。"},{"pid":"ed09dae260d34b8b9b06f41eae0cd84e7a4f61cd","tid":2460500,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T03:32:48.000Z","msg":"食草囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0f5a0cbf37a3041f63b0aa3c0c8c07c789d4805","tid":2460500,"uid":83910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T03:33:01.000Z","msg":"CONDOM <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b30166f161151ea3cb4a0f6dce003898a543cb4a","tid":2460500,"uid":106641,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T03:33:31.000Z","msg":"最恐怖係中原食人有時唔純粹係餓，可以係純粹為咗表忠，為咗恐嚇他人，重可以發展到研究人體邊部份點樣煮會好食，開人肉菜市場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n比起原始食人族部落有過之而無不及"},{"pid":"8886d9f0e2dcb098b67e892215ca21175cc7ada7","tid":2460500,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T03:35:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12f5052a517bb2513fef4bb0d0e0615904210816","tid":2460500,"uid":169801,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"d0f1760ee12b7e65caa42a216ccc95e74592a4d3","tid":2460500,"uid":59511,"like":64,"dislike":0,"score":64,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T01:39:27.000Z","msg":"的確，中國人係唔食談判呢一套，佢哋接受嘅係強權單方面壓迫。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T03:42:05.000Z","msg":"支那人就係鐘意食子彈，邊個唔比子彈佢食既，佢就當邊個係廢柴紙老虎"},{"pid":"b1a07115b8facbc4b0e248ceb65a4dc0718030cd","tid":2460500,"uid":60868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T03:47:09.000Z","msg":"吃八國聯軍啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25d24815a85cc64d13a7494f72013f8070746b60","tid":2460500,"uid":143526,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T03:48:20.000Z","msg":"蝙蝠"},{"pid":"264d2eb161c1e6acfcbc5be2973888ef1ff210f0","tid":2460500,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T03:49:18.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">草！</span><br />\n<br />\n你真的不懂？"},{"pid":"74b316f2e56e51a33e23b238ef7498c5f91cc815","tid":2460500,"uid":264683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T03:49:22.000Z","msg":"中国人乜都hack<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11244268dd0f9f874ec81a2faa88b557277fab71","tid":2460500,"uid":147376,"like":1,"